          <div class="faq-header">
            <span class="faq-question">How simple is the initial setup?</span>
            <div class="faq-icon-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7.41 15.41L12 10.83l4.59 4.58L18 14l-6-6-6 6z"/></svg></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Setting up is exceptionally straightforward. You can initialize your digital branches in our portal in under 15 minutes, download and print your custom QR codes, and have customers joining lines immediately. No technical expertise or physical terminal changes are required.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 2 -->
        <div class="faq-item" id="faq-scale">
          <div class="faq-header">
            <span class="faq-question">Can the system scale to support hundreds of counters?</span>
            <div class="faq-icon-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7.41 15.41L12 10.83l4.59 4.58L18 14l-6-6-6 6z"/></svg></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Yes, absolutely. Our system is built on resilient, high-capacity cloud architecture. We actively support large university complexes, hospital clinics, and banking branches with hundreds of agents and thousands of daily tokens without any performance degradation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 3 -->
        <div class="faq-item" id="faq-integrations">
          <div class="faq-header">
            <span class="faq-question">Does this integrate with custom CRM and scheduling systems?</span>
            <div class="faq-icon-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7.41 15.41L12 10.83l4.59 4.58L18 14l-6-6-6 6z"/></svg></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Our Enterprise Plan offers access to comprehensive REST APIs and Webhook pipelines. This lets your engineering team sync real-time queue states and customer feedback directly with CRM software like Salesforce, HubSpot, or internal patient portals.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 4 -->
        <div class="faq-item" id="faq-security">
          <div class="faq-header">
            <span class="faq-question">What data security measures do you employ?</span>
            <div class="faq-icon-box"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M7.41 15.41L12 10.83l4.59 4.58L18 14l-6-6-6 6z"/></svg></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Data security is our top priority. We use HTTPS TLS 1.3 encryption for all data transiting our network, and AES-256 databases. We are fully GDPR and HIPAA compliant, ensuring that any patient queue entries and customer data logs are completely private and masked.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
